title: Putting Humans on Mars, with Mike Massimino – StarTalk All-Stars
description: What will it take to send people to Mars safely, and bring them home again? StarTalk All-Stars host Astro Mike Massimino and co-host Maeve Higgins find out from John Charles, the Chief Scientist at NASA’s Human Research Program.
author: feed@startalkradio.net (Neil deGrasse Tyson)
